= Hello.

My name is Andy Van Den Heuvel. A software architect with over 11 years of experience working
at [Optis](http://www.optis.be). I'm passionate about technology and eager to learn new things.

In the past, I worked for national and international organisations, including [3M](http://www.3m.com),
[AXA](https://www.axa.com/), [BNP Paribas Fortis](https://www.bnpparibasfortis.be), [BMW](http://www.bmw.com),
[Euroclear](https://www.euroclear.com), [Proximus](https://www.proximus.be) and [Toyota](http://www.toyota.com).

In my free time, I enjoy running and travelling around the world.
I am happily married to my wonderful wife. We live together in
[Antwerp, Belgium](https://www.google.com/maps/place/Antwerp,+Belgium).

